---
// Client-side language detection
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Multistream - Watch Multiple Streams Locally</title>
    <meta name="description" content="A desktop app that connects directly to Twitch and Kick. No servers in the middle, no tracking. Just the streams.">
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://usemultistream.vercel.app/en/">
    <script is:inline>
      var lang = navigator.language || navigator.userLanguage;
      if (lang && lang.toLowerCase().startsWith('pt')) {
        window.location.replace('/pt-br/');
      } else {
        window.location.replace('/en/');
      }
    </script>
    <meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0; url=/en/" />
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #0f1115;">
  </body>
</html>
